kpi.name: M5001C36

kpi_info.title: BTS CHANNEL ELEMENT HSPA UTILIZATION IN DL - CLASS 5
kpi_info.use: The counter shows how many utilization rate samples have been detected within the (>80 - 100)% class per downlink direction. Each utilization rate sample calculates the number of CEs in use in HSPA divided by the number of all available (licensed) channel elements. UPDATED:The counter is incremented when the sample of the utilization rate is within (>80 - 100)% class.
